 increases when applying plausible changes to\nthe model parameters, e.g., using a Salpeter instead of a Chabrier IMF or a\nadopting a sub-solar metallicity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Mar 2012 21:02:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 Mar 2012 08:14:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 19 Jul 2012 08:54:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
